The paper deals with the design of symbol level precoding for multiuser MISO broadcast channels, which is a problem in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses optimization techniques and convex reformulation, which are common in networking and communications (cs.NI). The paper also deals with interference management and signal processing, which are topics in signal processing (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses simulation results and loss analysis, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG).
